<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none;padding:0" id="NavFrame6"><div class="NavHead" style="font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left;background:#ddf;text-align:center;">Scientists<a class="NavToggle" id="NavToggle6" href="#">[show]</a></div><div class="NavContent plainlist" style="font-size: 105%; padding: 0.35em 0px 0.4em; text-align: center; display: none;"><div class="hlist">
