<p>Solving this <a href="/wiki/Differential_equation" title="Differential equation">differential equation</a>, we find that the motion is described by the function
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle x(t)=A\cos(\omega t+\varphi ),}">
