  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/4a3d1c966b09c91a9feca34771c91345ba8b62e7" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.505ex; width:33.186ex; height:6.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle Z_{m}={\sqrt {\left(2\omega _{0}\zeta \right)^{2}+{\frac {1}{\omega ^{2}}}(\omega _{0}^{2}-\omega ^{2})^{2}}}}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>is the absolute value of the <a href="/wiki/Mechanical_impedance" title="Mechanical impedance">impedance</a> or <a href="/wiki/Linear_response_function" title="Linear response function">linear response function</a> and
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \varphi =\arctan \left({\frac {2\omega \omega _{0}\zeta }{\omega ^{2}-\omega _{0}^{2}}}\right)+n\pi }">
