<p>Supposing the solution is of the form
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \,\!q_{s}(\tau )=A\mathrm {e} ^{\mathrm {i} (\omega \tau +\varphi )}.}">
