  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/f54f0a229a097a6bf3a6341cdc2bfe1653231ccb" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:17.767ex; height:3.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \,\!q_{s}(\tau )=A\mathrm {e} ^{\mathrm {i} (\omega \tau +\varphi )}.}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>Its derivatives from zero to 2nd order are
