<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle q_{s}=A\mathrm {e} ^{\mathrm {i} (\omega \tau +\varphi )},\ {\frac {\mathrm {d} q_{s}}{\mathrm {d} \tau }}=\mathrm {i} \omega A\mathrm {e} ^{\mathrm {i} (\omega \tau +\varphi )},\ {\frac {\mathrm {d} ^{2}q_{s}}{\mathrm {d} \tau ^{2}}}=-\omega ^{2}A\mathrm {e} ^{\mathrm {i} (\omega \tau +\varphi )}.}">
