<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Amplitude_part">Amplitude part</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Harmonic_oscillator&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Amplitude part">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Harmonic_oscillator_gain.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8f/Harmonic_oscillator_gain.svg/220px-Harmonic_oscillator_gain.svg.png" width="220" height="165" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8f/Harmonic_oscillator_gain.svg/330px-Harmonic_oscillator_gain.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8f/Harmonic_oscillator_gain.svg/440px-Harmonic_oscillator_gain.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="1024" data-file-height="768"></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Harmonic_oscillator_gain.svg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>Bode plot of the frequency response of an ideal harmonic oscillator.</div></div></div>
<p>Squaring both equations and adding them together gives
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \left.{\begin{array}{rcl}A^{2}(1-\omega ^{2})^{2}&amp;=&amp;\cos ^{2}\varphi \\[6pt](2\zeta \omega A)^{2}&amp;=&amp;\sin ^{2}\varphi \end{array}}\right\}\Rightarrow A^{2}[(1-\omega ^{2})^{2}+(2\zeta \omega )^{2}]=1.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mrow>
          <mo fence="true" stretchy="true" symmetric="true"></mo>
