      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle V(x_{0})}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/c1e14fd8d981e0c4c50d553845c7af7ed4cf32a6" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:5.98ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="V(x_{0})"></span> is a minimum, the first derivative evaluated at <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle x_{0}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
